#: apps/core/templates/core/home.html:199
msgid ""
"Turning raw data into insight, from exploratory analysis and statistical "
"modelling to production-grade pipelines."
msgstr ""
"Trasformare dati grezzi in conoscenza, dall'analisi esplorativa e "
"modellazione statistica a pipeline pronte per la produzione."

#: apps/core/templates/core/home.html:223
msgid "Machine Learning & AI"
msgstr "Machine Learning & AI"

#: apps/core/templates/core/home.html:225
msgid ""
"Designing and training models that generalise, from classical algorithms to "
"Deep Learning and Large Language Model systems."
msgstr ""
"Progettare e addestrare modelli che generalizzano, dagli algoritmi classici "
"al Deep Learning e ai sistemi basati su Large Language Model."

#: apps/core/templates/core/home.html:248
